  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "The lead author has been carrying out logicist AI R&D for three decades and can count, on one hand, systems that genuinely integrate automated reasoning with the full gamut of the main human-level cognitive operators, and with attention and perception understood in keeping with state-of-the-art cognitive science.",
    "It is even harder to find such systems that are rigorous and computationally implemented.",
    "This missing type of research is what the present section's heading refers to as a lacuna.",
    "Addressing this inadequacy is observed as important by others.",
    "For example, Dietz et al. (2022), when setting out desiderata for HCAI systems, include that such systems must exhibit a \"bodymind like model of operation to sense, recognize, think, and act\" (Dietz et al., 2022)."
  ],
